    <h2>Inspriation</h2>
    As IT Professionals we all have our fair share of password insecurities. We know that we can probably be doing a better job, we know the high level concepts: longer is better, adding puncuation and complexity helps; but the further we dive into "randomness" the less likely we are to remember, the more annoying it is to type and the more likely we are to write the password down. This tool aims to create easy to remember sentences, with just enough randomness that hopefully you'll be able to remember your new password. 
